&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-zsh" data-lang="zsh">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">optimus-manager --print-mode
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>ej: en mi caso responde:
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
